ShareAV - a new media sharing framework

Primary Objectives and status:
Upload and download media (audio, video)
View media privately
Share media publically or to a group
    Add to your own library for easier access
    Re-share
View media from other streams or sources:
    Last.fm
    Jamendo
    RSS feeds eg podcasts
    Radio Streams e.g. icecast
    Visualisations
User pages
    Shared Media
    Favourite media
Create and remove users
    Owner
    Admin
    Moderator
Create and remove friends 
Create and remove groups of friends
OAuth/OpenID authentication
REST interface
Live updates for comments for groups
Live updates for who's viewing media

Live broadcasting and recording! (use JS Audio API)
Live notifications of when broadcasting or recording starts
Live chat - IRC integrated - allow anonymous

Mobile via PhoneGap

Frontend: Static HTML + JS layer - suitable for non-PHP devices
Backend: PHP, ZF2 + a NoSQL db, REST
